  "detailed_description": "<i>Little did Cinnamon know...that the streets were a concrete jungle...!!</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356450/extras/d361472653ff9af476af521f912ab14a.avif?t=1718170449\" width=500 height=414 /></span><br><br><strong><i>[A Street Cat's Tale 2]</i></strong><br>follows Cinnamon, who wanders out the window in pursuit of a butterfly.<br>It is a Sokoban-based, narrative-led puzzle adventure game about the struggles of stray cats.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>In search of new locations</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356450/extras/b25428ed73a4154bf80264e38c0aa60d.poster.avif?t=1718170449\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356450/extras/b25428ed73a4154bf80264e38c0aa60d.webm?t=1718170449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356450/extras/b25428ed73a4154bf80264e38c0aa60d.mp4?t=1718170449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356450/extras/862d36a1680f6cdedd4f1cb8cb6c980c.poster.avif?t=1718170449\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356450/extras/862d36a1680f6cdedd4f1cb8cb6c980c.webm?t=1718170449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356450/extras/862d36a1680f6cdedd4f1cb8cb6c980c.mp4?t=1718170449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Cinnamon wakes up in a place he has never seen before, oblivious to what lies ahead of him...<br>Will his wandering ever end?<br>Will he find his owner?<br>Solve the puzzles in Cinnnamon's way as you advance into new locations.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fighting Hunger</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356450/extras/9dafe239f9acc804f958c28b5c905ee0.poster.avif?t=1718170449\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356450/extras/9dafe239f9acc804f958c28b5c905ee0.webm?t=1718170449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356450/extras/9dafe239f9acc804f958c28b5c905ee0.mp4?t=1718170449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356450/extras/45f644afe971604252e4a5f9cb0a744c.poster.avif?t=1718170449\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356450/extras/45f644afe971604252e4a5f9cb0a744c.webm?t=1718170449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356450/extras/45f644afe971604252e4a5f9cb0a744c.mp4?t=1718170449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Cinnamon is very busy and very hungry.<br>Garbage bins offer temporary relief but never quality food.<br>Venture around the neighborhood, hunt for mice, frogs and other prey.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Everyone has a story</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356450/extras/2482d98e925ea82c172b4e966077afaf.poster.avif?t=1718170449\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356450/extras/2482d98e925ea82c172b4e966077afaf.webm?t=1718170449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356450/extras/2482d98e925ea82c172b4e966077afaf.mp4?t=1718170449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356450/extras/89532ed3b94a447599e8c4ee50897118.poster.avif?t=1718170449\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356450/extras/89532ed3b94a447599e8c4ee50897118.webm?t=1718170449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356450/extras/89532ed3b94a447599e8c4ee50897118.mp4?t=1718170449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Explore the neighborhood, meet new characters and talk to them.<br>They will tell you more about themselves when provided with the right gifts.<br>Many adorable animals await you with their own little stories.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356450/extras/13b0a38949a1898f47e2328018850023.poster.avif?t=1718170449\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356450/extras/13b0a38949a1898f47e2328018850023.webm?t=1718170449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356450/extras/13b0a38949a1898f47e2328018850023.mp4?t=1718170449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Will Cinnamon make it home safely?<br>Play to find out!",
